headline.print_headline: Pennetta, Riske, Giorgi, Makarova Win in New Haven
headline.main: Pennetta, Riske, Giorgi, Makarova Win in New Haven

lead_paragraph: Flavia Pennetta of Italy beat Klara Koukalova of the Czech Republic 6-1, 6-3 on Sunday in the first round of the Connecticut Open.
